column2: Home Records and Results OPO NSW State Titles
Results of OPO NSW State Titles held at Ballina on 30 June 2007.
Luke O'Neill's 4th attempt Squat of 370kgs and Total of 875kgs were National records.
Steve Hubert's 2nd attempt Benchpress was a Masters O/55 National Record.
